Paul McCartney celebrated his 80th birthday surrounded by his famous friends and his daughter, fashion designer Stella, 50.In a clip shared to Stella’s seven million Instagram followers, Paul was cheered and applauded as he walked down the stairs to join his friends.A-list attendees included Amy Schumer, Liv Tyler and Orlando Bloom.In the caption, Stella wished her dad a Happy Birthday and revealed her sweet nickname for him.She penned: “We applaud you on your birthday, Papa Smurf x.”